{"tid":419682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又一單！iphone 8未用先爆開！","createTime":"2017-09-30T16:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T06:54:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8045657f700abf539c6ac868de19444da672192b","tid":419682,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"最近亞洲有兩單 iPhone 8 Plus 內部膨脹引致機身爆開的報告。最先被發現機身爆開是一位台灣用戶，他在使用 iPhone 8 Plus 五日之後充電時突然膨脹至機身突然爆開，而另一單則發生於日本，有用戶表示在購買 iPhone 8 Plus 新機開箱時，就發現機身已經爆開。蘋果稱已經收到報告並正調查事件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-09-30-13.09.51-694x435.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2017-09-30-13.09.51-694x435.png&h=f8bde73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次被發現問題的是最新推出的 iPhone 8 Plus。第一單報告發生於台灣，主機在充電時出現機身膨脹現象。根據機主表示，當時正利用原廠充電器及充電線，為主機充電，而主機只用了 5 日。主機在充電 5 分鐘後出現機身膨脹至爆裂的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-09-30-13.24.18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2017-09-30-13.24.18.png&h=5da3756d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而另一單則發生於日本。一位網名 @Magokoro0511 的用戶在 Twitter 上發表帖文，指他新購入的 iPhone 8 Plus 在開箱時已經出現機身膨脹現象。在圖片當中看到，主機中央部份脹起，熒幕左右兩方的固定裝置都已被翻開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-09-30-13.11.46-694x415.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2017-09-30-13.11.46-694x415.png&h=c0d2da48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據網站 PCMag 的評估，這兩部機的共通點是表面全無燒傷的痕跡，而根據日本案例，並非不妥的充電導致主機膨脹，或許是黏合屏幕的膠水或螺絲導致上述事件發生，但亦有可能是更廣泛的問題導致。而 Thenextweb 網站測評估此次問題與電池有關，今次 iPhone 8 Plus 所採用的電池正是由 ATL (Amperex Technology Limited) 供應。<br />\n<br />\n而蘋果則指已經收到用戶的報告，現時正調查事件起因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/09/30/iphone8pluspopup/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2Fiphone8pluspopup%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=wP3koozxvDs1WiWs1vL7wk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ee3e08e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/09/30/iphone8pluspopup/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"cdb58ff7e5bcdad8c02eb068ec780eb7872aa5bb","tid":419682,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d704c78ad0063e628e4b099c2e76d4f6cf5ee3c","tid":419682,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"HK Regon :<br />\n<br />\nNo Refund<br />\n<br />\nNo Return<br />\n<br />\nNo Service<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0670b2af76c203fa09562d4e199dcd32cb48cbd5","tid":419682,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Apple Retail Store 購買政策</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據本購買政策，所有從香港 Apple Retail Store 購買的產品<span style=\"color: red;\">不得退貨或換貨</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/legal/sales_policies/retail.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Flegal%2Fsales_policies%2Fretail.html&d=wP3koozxvDs1WiWs1vL7wk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=9a7952e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/legal/sales_policies/ret